Module org.myjtools.jexten

module org.myjtools.jexten
Core module of the JExten extension framework.

This module provides the fundamental API for defining and discovering extensions in a modular Java application. It includes:

  • @Extension and @ExtensionPoint annotations for marking extension classes
  • ExtensionManager for discovering and retrieving extension instances
  • Scope and Priority enums for controlling extension lifecycle and ordering
  • InjectionProvider and ExtensionLoader for custom dependency injection integration
